text: Renée Govaert (born 25 January 1962) is a Belgian rower. She competed in the women's double sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Belgium Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
